{"tid":42360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[台灣人也是支那人]有閩南話唔講講普通話?","createTime":"2016-12-16T15:17:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-02T17:56:48.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8411c10466b7fcc1788ead0ecaf2435add8da2aa","tid":42360,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T15:17:20.000Z","msg":"真係收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講經濟, 個台灣股巿樓巿完全不值一提 <br />\n<br />\n講道德, D風化案僅次於印度 <br />\n<br />\n講音樂娛樂, 果D周姐倫講埋D普通話梅下梅下, 真係垃圾都不如, 有本土語言唔識用黎填詞, 唔會用黎做電影/電視對白 <br />\n<br />\n之前仲睇到個post, D台仔笑香港D數學簡單 <br />\n我心諗呢D咁既意識形態咁似羅湖橋以北D人既?咁大個鼻又唔諗下自己好樣衰<br />\n<br />\n老老豆豆, 台灣人咪又係支那種,係行為上同思想上都同大陸人一樣分唔到架啦, 只不過係寫繁體字的支那人, 咪睇到自己咁高啦D台支"},{"pid":"34d71f2e64732a7e84772442ee382c4383a5b435","tid":42360,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T15:22:19.000Z","msg":"留名睇樓主俾人話分化"},{"pid":"2a8ffd85fc9c9607428ba30d55e2f8ddc32963e5","tid":42360,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T15:23:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名睇樓主俾人話分化</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n補充：同埋話樓主玩lol"},{"pid":"834735dd6a488b1aaca5b38c2f93cc05f7c6770a","tid":42360,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T15:37:51.000Z","msg":"講普通話同國語嘅都係支那狗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"415e16e5f61ccce2c517756713d09d43c18ff45b","tid":42360,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T16:49:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ba6531a52ee59684d8dec18fd9501a25539519","tid":42360,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T18:22:20.000Z","msg":"大部分認同<br />\n<br />\nbut 1.周姐倫巧天<br />\n<br />\n      2.香港人都係支那種"},{"pid":"331cd5586bd6ff319888f81bd2f8e9aa0cafe8a5","tid":42360,"uid":61104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T20:28:39.